{
  "stem": "26111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was-- the level was too low under those circumstances-- and went to evening classes, had a job in the meantime, and took the-- took the matriculation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as soon as I could, I was going to enter university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I took more courses to prepare me for that while I was on the land, did a lot of reading, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, an opportunity presented itself to join a corps that the US Intelligence was putting together, which was called the Disarmament Division, part of the US Army Air Force.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin by marriage-- the brother of my, my cousin, who was also a refugee about my age-- a little older-- in fact, he's about five years older-- he was also in England.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He married the daughter of a Jewish couple there that-- from Germany that had also landed there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her brother had gone to America and was now in the army and was back in England in uniform.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told me about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I immediately enlisted his help, and-- as far as he could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I made my application.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was at last, I was going to be in-- at my post in, in Germany a little before the armistice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the armistice happened a few days too early.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I only got there after the armistice-- middle of May, a few days after the-- armistice was, I think, the 8th of May of, of '45.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
